```{r pancreas 32591464, include=FALSE}

PMID_32591464 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32591464', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32591464 <- paste0(PMID_32591464$journal,' ', PMID_32591464$year, ' ', PMID_32591464$month,';', PMID_32591464$volume,'(', PMID_32591464$number,'):', PMID_32591464$pages)

PubMed_32591464 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32591464$eprint)

doi_32591464 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32591464$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
